She came to my home.
Our daughters saw her.

11
00:00:21,179 --> 00:00:23,499
You blew up my life!

12
00:00:23,620 --> 00:00:25,608
Reggie Ledoux.
Where is he?

13
00:00:25,687 --> 00:00:27,483
He only cook
for one client now.

14
00:00:27,582 --> 00:00:28,632
