I had deals with 'em when
I was working narco.

17
00:00:33,737 --> 00:00:34,952
We can get to Ledoux.

18
00:00:35,042 --> 00:00:37,867
Keep this handy and be listening to
Beaumont police channels.

19
00:00:37,999 --> 00:00:38,914
You got it?

20
00:00:39,042 --> 00:00:41,035
I got it. Are you
gonna be all right?

21
00:00:41,300 --> 00:00:42,927
I need a good soldier.

22
00:00:43,133 --> 00:00:44,872
Now, you do this with us,

23
00:00:44,992 --> 00:00:46,859
