puttin' you with my man.

24
00:00:46,985 --> 00:00:47,855
Don't fire.

25
00:00:47,941 --> 00:00:49,174
Do not--

26
00:00:51,236 --> 00:00:52,538
What are you doing, man?

27
00:00:52,902 --> 00:00:55,919
Marty, I need you.
90 seconds!

28
00:00:56,143 --> 00:00:57,304
Go, go, go!

